---
title: Cheesy Monterey Jack Burgers with Garlic and Rosemary Foil-Pouch Potatoes
description: Grab the cooler and get ready to hit the grill! Delight your tastebuds with this Monterey Jack and fig topped rosemary burger. An elegant side of garlic grilled potatoes rounds out this long weekend winner!
